{"tid":2445330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緬甸部隊阻撓救護車駛近  引致示威者傷重不治","createTime":"2021-03-13T14:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T21:51:41.000Z","uid":227801,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"92baa9edc556aefd10b686dfe7aa1713e6a49f2e","tid":2445330,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:14:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580437-20210313.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580437-20210313.htm&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfMkuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=9920b4de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580437-20210313.htm&h=f325e7c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580437-20210313.htm</a><br />\n緬甸反軍方示威持續，保安部隊繼續武力鎮壓，昨晚至今天，至少6人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n根據目擊者和當地傳媒報道，在第二大城市曼德勒，警員向靜坐人士開槍，3人喪生，多人受傷。在中部城鎮卑謬，一人死亡。在最大城市仰光，民眾昨晚在一間警局外示威，要求釋放被捕人士時，警員開槍，兩人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">卑謬一名示威者告訴路透社，保安部隊最初不准救護車駛近傷者，其後才放行，但其中一名傷者最終傷重不治。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n美國國務院說，鑑於緬甸多處地方出現人道危機，滯留美國的緬甸國民或居民，可以根據臨時保護身份暫時留低。他們初步可以逗留18個月，國土安全部估計，大約有1600人符合暫留資格。"},{"pid":"2c835ceab4b9805f15b91ca6726e77aeb524ec02","tid":2445330,"uid":80072,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:15:32.000Z","msg":"似曾相識"},{"pid":"d3d81e6586645e1e5d718c5932179a36cd192b37","tid":2445330,"uid":227801,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"2c835ceab4b9805f15b91ca6726e77aeb524ec02","tid":2445330,"uid":80072,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:15:32.000Z","msg":"似曾相識"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:16:00.000Z","msg":"尚德<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec751733aa52a05a2710605bf3e225b3f3331fc9","tid":2445330,"uid":47356,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"d3